<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="operation-n">operation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌɒpə'reɪʃn/    美 /ˌɑːpə'reɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 运转；运行；操作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are three lifts <strong>in operation</strong>.
有3部电梯在运行。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You must read the operation instructions before using this machine.
在使用这台机器之前你必须阅读操作说明书。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 经营；运营：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>meetings concerning all the aspects of hotel operation
关于酒店运营各方面的会议</p><footer>2010 上海</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The new plant is scheduled to <strong>go / come into operation</strong> in May this year.
新工厂计划今年5月投入运营。</p></div>

<h4 id="3c">3.<strong>[C] 企业；团体：</strong></h4>
<p>a business company：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a huge multinational electronics operation
一家大型跨国电子公司</p></div>

<h4 id="4-c">4.★ <strong>[C] 手术：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s recovering from an <strong>operation on</strong> his shoulder.
他肩膀动了手术，正在恢复中。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Often, if a person is in an accident, or <strong>has an operation</strong>, he will lose a lot of blood.
通常来说，如果一个人出事故或者动手术，会大量失血。</p></div>

<h4 id="5-c">5.★ <strong>[C] 行动：</strong></h4>
<p>an activity, often highly organized, that involves many people, actions, days, etc.：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>UN rescue operations
联合国营救行动</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police have launched a major operation against drug.
警方发起了一场大规模的缉毒行动。</p></div>

<h4 id="6-c">6.★ <strong>[C] (计算机的) 运算；操作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>perform various mathematical operations
进行各种数学运算</p><footer>2012 北京</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="put-into-operation">put ... into operation</h3>
<p>1.<strong>实施；使…运转；启用：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s time to put our plan into operation.
现在应该实施我们的计划了。</p></div></div>